name: 'Abracadabra' 07.08.2019
description:
An isometric illusion that will leave the viewer perplexed.

Created by Tiago Hands, a mathematical artist based in the United Kingdom.

Tiago Hands currently runs a Youtube channel with 4,560 subscribers and an Instagram account based on geometric proofs with another 38,700 organic followers.

Since January 2014 he not only has been sharing geometric proofs with the world, but also geometric art.

This piece itself garnered 392 likes on his personal Instagram account.
